{
  "stem": "10406.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe not play per se, we were still out on the street because the atmosphere was already tense, and they did have German, you know, policing the streets, even though you didn't have the main army body there.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what happened is as soon as the SS moved in, they issued an order that all Jewish males from 16 to 60 should report to the center of town in order to change passports.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was part-- that's when they--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's the same group.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Einsatzgruppen are basically the SS that came in with-- with that purpose.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And whoever doesn't report would be shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the next morning, most-- many of the people reported.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And for some reason again, I was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was too young yet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wasn't old enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to be, you know, 16 and up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a lot of people that had to go didn't go because the feeling was that it's not a good feeling.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the men reported, and when I got there, I saw men lined up in the middle of the street in rows of maybe 8 or 10 and down the road.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember looking at one particular man who was a friend of our family, and his face was so pale-- like, you could see, practically read, the fright in his face.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I noticed the German-- you know, they had the SS there with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had what I found out later was gestapo with brown-- brown collars and brown insignia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had soldiers and officers in black uniforms, which were the SS or, like, the secret police.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
